>> time required: 20 minutes
>> course: apero

Fry sliced @leek{1} and sliced @mushrooms{5} in @oil{1%tbsp} in #frying pan{}.
Let cool ~{10%minutes}
Mix @madame loik echalote{1 container}, juice of @lemon{1/2}, @curry powder{1/2%tsp}, @mustard{1%tsp}, and @salt{1%pinch} with the leek / mushroom mixture
